FBIS4-12494 "drnes069_s_94015" FBIS-NES-94-069 Daily Report 10 Apr 1994 Iran Majles Passes Bill To Merge Three Ministries Majles Passes Bill To Merge Three Ministries LD1004161194 Tehran Voice of the Islamic Republic of Iran First Program Network in Persian 0930 GMT 10 Apr 94 LD1004161194 Tehran Voice of the Islamic Republic of Iran First Program Network Persian BFN [Excerpt] The bill on merging the Ministries of Industry, Heavy Industry, and Mines and Metals, and the formation of the Ministry of Mines and Industry, was approved in today's open session of the Islamic Consultative Majles. [passage omitted]
